You are helping build Atlas, an AI-powered career readiness web app.

Product scope:
- Analyze a resume against a target job description.
- Generate a role-fit report and 30/60/90-day roadmap.
- Keep v1 focused: no auth, no payments, no LinkedIn scraping, no job-board integrations.

Engineering standards:
- Keep AI logic server-side.
- Never expose API keys in client code.
- Validate user input before calling the AI provider.
- Validate AI output before rendering.
- Write tests for validation, prompt construction, and output schema handling.
- Avoid storing resume or job description content in v1.

Design standards:
- Follow a clean professional interface.
- Use Inter, white/soft gray backgrounds, restrained blue accent, thin borders, and 6-12px radius components.
- Build the usable app first, not a marketing-only landing page.

